Установка composer
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-and-use-composer-on-ubuntu-18-04

Запуск composer
php /usr/local/bin/composer

Добавление пакетов, если ошбика composer install
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35815376/to-enable-extensions-verify-that-they-are-enabled-in-those-ini-files-vagrant
apt-get install php7.2 libapache2-mod-php7.2 php7.2-common php7.2-gd php7.2-mysql php7.2-curl php7.2-intl php7.2-xsl php7.2-mbstring php7.2-zip php7.2-bcmath php7.2-soap php-xdebug php-imagick


Run these command after going into the /web folder:
sudo chgrp www-data ./assets
and
sudo chmod g+w ./assets/

